 Gemini CLI\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://geminicli.com/docs/troubleshooting/\\\"},{\\\"title\\\":\\\"hangs indefinitely when executed from Node.js `child_process` (subprocess) · Issue #6715 · google-gemini/gemini-cli\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/issues/6715\\\"},{\\\"title\\\":\\\"Ctrl+f to interact with a shell NOT WORKING (windows) · Issue #14296 · google-gemini/gemini-cli\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/issues/14296\\\"},{\\\"title\\\":\\\"Error No input provided via stdin, Node.js (v22.17.1) · Issue #4999 · google-gemini/gemini-cli\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/issues/4999\\\"},{\\\"title\\\":\\\"CLI gets stuck at “Awaiting Further Direction” with no way to proceed except ESC · Issue #3617 · google-gemini/gemini-cli\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/issues/3617\\\"},{\\\"title\\\":\\\"How to run /command from script · google-gemini/gemini-cli · Discussion #5381\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/discussions/5381\\\"}]\\n\\nBased on the search results, there are several known issues with Gemini CLI hanging when waiting for input. Here's a summary of the relevant findings:\\n\\n## Known Issues\\n\\n### 1. Agent Hangs on Interactive Shell Prompts (Issue #10909)\\nWhen the Gemini CLI agent runs commands that trigger interactive shell prompts (yes/no, enter a name, overwrite file, etc.), the agent becomes stuck and never progresses.(no content)The agent hangs indefinitely when a command requests interactive input. No fallback, timeout, or guidance is provided. No clear way to resume or supply the needed input.\\n\\n**Workarounds:**\\n- Manually aborting with Ctrl+C / Esc.\\n- Passing -y/--force where supported.\\n\\n### 2. Subprocess/Non-TTY Hang (Issue #6715)\\nGemini CLI version 0.1.22 hangs indefinitely when executed from Node.js child_process (subprocess), while the exact same commands work perfectly when run directly from a terminal.(no content)This regression breaks: Automation tools that spawn Gemini CLI as subprocess, MCP servers using Gemini CLI backend, CI/CD pipelines with Gemini CLI integration, and any programmatic usage of Gemini CLI.\\n\\n**Workaround:** Close stdin immediately after spawning:\\n```javascript\\nchild.stdin.end();  // CRITICAL: Close stdin immediately to prevent hang\\n```\\n\\n### 3. Windows-Specific Issues (Issue #13549, #14296)\\nThe CLI enters a \\\"zombie\\\" state where it becomes completely unresponsive. It often hangs at \\\"Connecting to MCP servers... (3/4)\\\", waiting indefinitely. When it reaches the input prompt (> Type your message), it refuses to accept any keyboard input.(no content)Running Windows 11 with Gemini 0.18.4, users are getting stuck on \\\"Interactive shell awaiting input... press Ctrl+f to focus shell\\\" - pressing that combo does nothing. So can't use gemini cli due to this.\\n\\n### 4. CI Environment Detection Issue\\nThe Gemini CLI does not enter interactive mode (no prompt appears) if an environment variable starting with CI_ (e.g., CI_TOKEN) is set. This is because the is-in-ci package, used by the underlying UI framework, detects these variables and assumes a non-interactive CI environment.\\n\\n**Solution:** If the CI_ prefixed variable is not needed for the CLI to function, you can temporarily unset it for the command. e.g., `env -u CI_TOKEN gemini`\\n\\n### 5. False Positive \\\"Awaiting Input\\\" (Issue #15835)\\nDuring long-running processes, specifically the \\\"preflight\\\" check, the CLI displays the message: \\\"interactive shell awaiting input\\\" However, no user input is actually required. If the process is left alone for approximately 30 seconds, the message disappears and the preflight checks continue as expected.\\n\\n## Debugging Tips\\nUse the --debug flag for more detailed output. In interactive mode, press F12 to view the debug console.\\n\\n\\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks.\"}]},\"uuid\":\"b3addf3e-b5aa-4903-b292-f2d125152570\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-18T20:48:24.198Z\",\"toolUseResult\":{\"query\":\"gemini cli hangs waiting for input interactive prompt stdin\",\"results\":[{\"tool_use_id\":\"srvtoolu_01S3qZYhtimBVtgTwwMK9cR2\",\"content\":[{\"title\":\"Agent hangs on interactive shell prompts (e.g., npx shadcn@latest add button and npm run dev) · Issue #10909 · google-gemini/gemini-cli\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/issues/10909\"},{\"title\":\"CLI Hangs/Unresponsive at Input Prompt on Windows 11 (Nightly 0.18.0) · Issue #13549 · google-gemini/gemini-cli\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/issues/13549\"},{\"title\":\"Stuck at Interactive shell awaiting input · Issue #14364 · google-gemini/gemini-cli\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/issues/14364\"},{\"title\":\"False positive \\\"interactive shell awaiting input\\\" message during long-running preflight checks · Issue #15835 · google-gemini/gemini-cli\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/issues/15835\"},{\"title\":\"Troubleshooting guide | Gemini CLI\",\"url\":\"https://geminicli.com/docs/troubleshooting/\"},{\"title\":\"hangs indefinitely when executed from Node.js `child_process` (subprocess) · Issue #6715 · google-gemini/gemini-cli\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/issues/6715\"},{\"title\":\"Ctrl+f to interact with a shell NOT WORKING (windows) · Issue #14296 · google-gemini/gemini-cli\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/issues/14296\"},{\"title\":\"Error No input provided via stdin, Node.js (v22.17.1) · Issue #4999 · google-gemini/gemini-cli\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini-cli/issues/4999\"},{\"title\":\"CLI gets stuck at “Awaiting Further Direction” with no way to proceed except ESC · Issue #3617 · google-gemini/gemini-cli\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/google-gemini/gemini